                     <p> WEDNESBURY. <persName>
                           <forename>Adam</forename> de <surname>Hamwolde</surname>
                        </persName>
               grants to <persName>
                           <forename>Richard</forename> de <surname>Scrinklinge</surname>
                        </persName>, 
               son of <persName nymRef="Scrinklinge">
                           <forename>Robert</forename>
                        </persName>, and to 
                  <persName nymRef="Scrinklinge">
                           <forename>Matilda</forename> his wife</persName>, and to
                  <persName nymRef="Scrinklinge">
                           <forename>John</forename> his eldest son</persName> 
                  for 17s. one half acre of land of his tenement of 
                  <placeName type="minor">Hamwolde</placeName> lying in the parish of 
               <placeName key="place_108630">Wednesberghe at Suthamwolde</placeName>. 
                  Dated September, <origDate>9 Ed. [I]</origDate>. 
                
               . <!--WAS Ch. 192--></p>
